abstract: Venus and Serena Williams are both on entry list for BNP Paribas Open tennis tournament, one year after Serena ended 14-year boycott.
lead_paragraph: A year after her sister Serena played Indian Wells for the first time in 14 years, Venus Williams is on the entry list for the event in March.

headline.print_headline: Sports Briefing | Tennis; Venus Williams to Return
headline.main: Venus Williams Enters Indian Wells Tournament, Signaling End of Boycott
